rows.label: qst502017_msg0001
rows.name:
You look pretty tired, Chancellor.
Would you like me to give you a
shoulder massage?

rows.label: qst502017_msg0002
rows.name:
Why, that's very kind of you.
I'd appreciate it, thank you.

rows.label: qst502017_msg0004
rows.name:
Ahhhhhh, that was the best
massage I've ever had!

rows.label: qst502017_msg0005
rows.name:
I think that tingly sparking sensation
may have given my old joints a whole
new lease on life!

rows.label: qst502017_msg0006
rows.name:
My granddaughter's massages always
make me feel like I'm a year younger...

rows.label: qst502017_msg0007
rows.name:
But yours make me feel like
I've lost at least twenty!

rows.label: qst502017_msg0008
rows.name:
Well, I'm happy you liked it so much!
Would you like me to do it again?

rows.label: qst502017_msg0009
rows.name:
That's a very tempting proposition,
but I wouldn't want to keep you for
too long.

rows.label: qst502017_msg0010
rows.name:
Besides, if I were to lose forty years,
I'd be younger than His Majesty!

rows.label: qst502017_msg0013
rows.name:
N-no, that's quite all right, thank you!
I have a feeling something terrible
will happen if I accept!
